title: Exploration of Energization and Radiation in Geospace (ERG) Medium Energy Particle experiments - ion mass analyzer (MEP-i) Level-2 3D flux data - Shoichiro Yokota (Osaka University)

info.x_cadence_note: Counts based on variable 'epoch' in https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/sp_phys/data/erg/mepi/l2/3dflux/2017/erg_mepi_l2_3dflux_20170324_v01_03.cdf. The most common cadence occurred for 40.6455% of the 869 timesteps. Cadence = 15984560000 [ns] = PT15.98456S.
